high_descs: Turn to the left and go to the counter that has the microwave on it.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter by the apple.
Turn around and go to the dining table.
Use the knife to cut the loaf of bread into slices.
Move to the right at the dining table in front of the plate.
Put the knife down on the table by the bread.
Move to the left at the dining table in front of the bread.
Pick up a slice of the bread.
Turn to the right and go to the counter that has the microwave on it.
Put the bread inside the microwave and turn it on to cook, remove the bread when it is done.
Turn around and go to the dining table where the butter knife is.
Put the bread on the table next to the butter knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked piece of bread on the table.

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to the apple to the left of the microwave.
Pick up the knife under the apple.
Turn to your right and walk in the direction of the sink, hang a right and walk to the round table to the right of the fridge, stand to the right of the chair at the table.
Slice the brown loaf of bread on the table.
Move to your right so that you are standing in front of the gray bottle and the tan bowl.
Place the knife on the loaf of bread.
Move nearer to the chair to your left.
Pick up the end slice of bread nearest you.
Turn right and carry the bread slice to the microwave oven.
Open the microwave door, place the bread to the left of the gray turntable, close the door, turn the microwave on; after cooking open the microwave door, pick up the bread slice, close the door.
Turn around and walk to the round table and stand near the chair.
Place the heated slice of bread on the table next to the end of the loaf of bread closest to you.
anns.task_desc: Slice a loaf of bread, heat a slice, bring it back to the table

high_descs: turn left and face the counter top near the microwave
pick up the knife on the tomato
turn around and head straight to the kitchen table opposite the counter top
shift the bread slightly away from the coffee maker
face the kitchen table with the bread on top
Make one slice of bread and place the knife on top
face the kitchen table with the single slice
pick up the slice of bread
walk to the microwave directly opposite the kitchen table
open the microwave door and place the bread inside to heat for several seconds, then remove the bread
take the bread slice back to the kitchen table with the loaf
place the slice of bread below the knife
anns.task_desc: Slice a piece of bread and warm it up
